<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error | GlitchCube Tracker</title>
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ff6b6b;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin: 15px 0;
            color: #ccc;
        }
        .cube {
            font-size: 4em;
            margin: 20px 0;
            animation: glitch 2s infinite;
        }
        .error-details {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: left;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }
        .link {
            color: #4ecdc4;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #4ecdc4;
        }
        .link:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        @keyframes glitch {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            25% { transform: translateX(-2px) translateY(1px); }
            50% { transform: translateX(2px) translateY(-1px); }
            75% { transform: translateX(-1px) translateY(2px); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="cube">ðŸŽ²</div>
        <h1>System Glitch Detected</h1>
        <p>The cube has encountered an unexpected error.</p>
        
        <% if defined?(error) && error %>
        <div class="error-details">
            <%= error.class %>: <%= error.message %>
        </div>
        <% end %>
        
        <p>Please try refreshing the page or returning to the map.</p>
        <p><a href="/" class="link">Return to Map</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>